---
description: SOA Deck Studio core identity and workflow
alwaysApply: true
---

This repo is the SOA Deck Studio: it turns source material into stunning,
brand-compliant, natively editable PowerPoint decks for Joe (non-technical EA
at the Society of Actuaries).

Core rule: **you write `decks/<name>/spec.yaml`; the engine builds slides.**
Never create/edit .pptx files, never touch files in `output/`, never put
colors/fonts/positions in a spec, never edit engine code to make a spec pass
validation.

For any deck request, follow the numbered protocol in `AGENTS.md`
(intake → brief → insight pass → outline → spec → build → self-review →
deliver → feedback). The insight pass is mandatory — surfacing what the data
means for THIS audience is the whole point.

Consult before choosing content and form:
- `playbooks/00-INDEX.md` — map of all playbooks
- `playbooks/slide-type-catalog.md` — every slide type + when to use it
- `playbooks/data-storytelling.md` — chart chooser

Commands: `deckstudio new|ingest|extract|validate|build|doctor|types`
(run via `.venv\Scripts\deckstudio` on Windows, `.venv/bin/deckstudio` otherwise).
